nd `rrt` metrics. This degradation spans across services like `paymentservice`, `shippingservice`, and `cartservice`.\n\n### Top 3 significant metrics\nBased on the absolute change ratio during the fault period:\n1. `node_filesystem_usage_rate`\n2. `rrt_max` (affecting `paymentservice`, `shippingservice`, etc.)\n3. `rrt` (affecting multiple services)\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_filesystem_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-01\",\n      \"reason\": \"The node experienced severe filesystem usage exhaustion, indicated by an increase in node_filesystem_usage_rate from 50.98% to 71.43%. This is likely causing downstream impact on pods and services hosted on the node.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Filesystem usage rate median increased by 33.41%. P99 reached 93.8% from a normal state of 71.48%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service degraded due to backend infrastructure issues or resource bottlenecks. Notable metrics include rrt_max increasing from a normal median of 1936ms to 2258ms and P99 exceeding 63825ms.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median relative changes observed: +15.36%, P99 change ratio +174.54%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service latency increase possibly due to resource contention or dependency failures. rrt_max rose significantly during the anomaly period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Shippingservice rtt_max increased from 1883ms to 1915ms; P99 spiked to 75548.8ms.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据调用链数据分析，我们发现多个显著的异常调用链，具体如下：\n\n1. **CartService与Redis之间的显著延迟**:\n   - `cartservice-0 -> cartservice-0 (operation: HMSET)`: 延迟倍数为约 17 倍 (1573ms -> 26842ms)\n   - `cartservice-2 -> cartservice-2 (operation: HMSET)`: 延迟倍数为约 8.4 倍 (1361ms -> 11438ms)\n\n2. **从Frontend到CartService的显著延迟**:\n   - `frontend-0 -> cartservice-2 (POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem)`: 延迟倍数为约 5.1 倍 (3583ms -> 18480ms)\n   - `frontend-0 -> frontend-0 (hipstershop.CartService/AddItem)`: 延迟倍数为约 3.8 倍 (5216ms -> 20118ms)\n   - `frontend-1 -> cartservice-2 (POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart)`: 延迟倍数为约 4.3 倍 (2310ms -> 9886ms)\n   - `frontend-1 -> frontend-1 (hipstershop.CartService/GetCart)`: 延迟倍数为约 2.9 倍 (3932ms -> 11358ms)\n\n3. **Frontend到CheckoutService的显著延迟**:\n   - `frontend-0 -> frontend-0 (hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder)`: 延迟倍数为约 1.7 倍 (148672ms -> 252029ms)\n\n4. **RecommendationService与Frontend的异常延迟**:\n   - `frontend-2 -> frontend-2 (hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations)`: 延迟倍数显著 (142454ms -> 8831ms) 这里是正常过程显得异常快\n\n5. **RecommendationService与ProductCatalog的异常延迟**:\n   - `recommendationservice-2 -> recommendationservice-2 (/hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/ListProducts)`: 延迟倍数约 1.3 倍 (2779ms -> 3667ms)\n\n从以上的信息中，我们可以看出：\n- **根因可能涉及Redis的性能问题**，与CartService的调用显著受影响。\n- **Frontend中的调用链也出现显著延迟**，可能是网络问题或由Redis问题间接引起。\n- **CheckoutService与RecommendationService延迟可能是次要影响**，需要进一步检查如果也是频繁异常的话，可能与总体网络性能有关。\n\n接下来是总结的 JSON 输出：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"cartservice-0->cartservice-0\",\n    \"cartservice-2->cartservice-2\",\n    \"frontend-0->cartservice-2\",\n    \"frontend-0->frontend-0\",\n    \"frontend-1->cartservice-2\",\n    \"frontend-1->frontend-1\",\n    \"frontend-0->frontend-0\",\n    \"frontend-2->frontend-2\",\n    \"recommendationservice-2->recommendationservice-2\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"高延迟 spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"如 cartservice-0 到 cartservice-0 (正常: 1573ms, 异常: 26842ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"从Frontend的请求延迟显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"如 frontend-0 到 cartservice-2 (正常: 3583ms, 异常: 18480ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService与ProductCatalog\